The Auspah are a race mentioned in Imcandoria's fall. They supposedly lived in and around the area where Imcandoria stood in the far north. Little is known about them, but they are associated with fire, being particularly interested in fiery jewellery forged by the giants from the Forge of the Giants.

The race originated in RuneScape, where they are an ancient race of humanoids wielding power over fire, hailing from the world Muspell. By the end of the Second Age the race was almost wiped out, with only one single individual having survived to this day.

The '''Auspah''' are a race mentioned in [[Imcandoria's fall]]. They supposedly lived in and around the area where [[Imcandoria]] stood in the far north. Little is known about them, but they are associated with fire, being particularly interested in fiery jewellery forged by the [[giant]]s from the Forge of the Giants.

The race originated in ''RuneScape'', where they are an ancient race of humanoids wielding power over fire, hailing from the world {{RSL|Muspell}}. By the end of the [[Second Age]] the race was almost wiped out, with only {{RSL|Char|one single individual}} having survived to this day.
